Subject: [Rcpp-devel] Dispatching based on SEXPTYPE
In-Reply-To: <CABdHhvHQOnAT=20fFgF+LYN4vaHc0UTrjsxwzdZzyj1ywjYNhQ@mail.gmail.com>
References: <CABdHhvE9Yq3jzfkmYkpAfXNCDpdP=9FJyFCLzjotk-_7a87MBQ@mail.gmail.com>
